metadata.name: RAMLA & SABAH
metadata.description:
3D Ilustration and Visual Art
1080 x 1080

Ramla (prophet, sand)
Sabah (born in the morning)

We all have deep roots that bind us to a origin, such as family roots. Of them we should feel proud but you are not a tree, you can decide to move and take root in another
place.

As one moves into the future, the way loudest and 
clearest way to do it is if you have a good sense of 
its past and origin.

There are only two lasting legacies we can hope for
give our children. One of them is roots, the another, wings to fly high.
